{"word":"G1762 - ἔνι - éni - en'-ee - Be","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔνι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">éni</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en'-ee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"என்றிரு - படர்க்கை ஒருமை"},{"paragraph":"is in, is among, has place, is present"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Contracted for third person singular present indicative of <a href=\"#/G1751 - ἔνειμι - éneimi - en'-i-mee/1751\">G1751</a>; impersonally <i>there is</i> in or among: - be, (there) is.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}